---
<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
</head>
<body>
<Header />
<main class="about-content">
    <h2>About Us</h2>
    <p>
        ACM at NCSU is the student chapter of the <a href="https://www.acm.org/" target="_blank">Association for Computing Machinery</a> at North Carolina State University.
        ACM is the world's largest educational and scientific computing organization.
    </p>
    <p>
        We're dedicated to building an inclusive community of computing students, academics, and professionals
        at NC State. Students and faculty from any discipline with an interest in computing are welcome to 
        attend ACM at NCSU events and join us in fostering curiosity in the computational sciences.
    </p>
    <p>
        We focus on introducing new students to the breadth of computer science while helping upperclassmen advance 
        their careers through networking events, skill-building workshops, and internship connections.
    </p>
    <p>
        You can get involved in ACM at NCSU by attending our variety of
        events, including socials, educational talks, and industry networking sessions.
        At these events, you'll meet a diverse group of students passionate about
        computing, along with professors and industry leaders.
    </p>

    <h2>Leadership</h2>
    
    <h3 class="subsection-title">Executive Board</h3>
    <div class="board-grid">
        {executiveBoard.map(member => {
            const CardWrapper = member.website ? 'a' : 'div';
            const cardProps = member.website 
                ? { href: member.website, target: "_blank", rel: "noopener noreferrer" }
                : {};
            
            return (
                <CardWrapper 
                    class={`member-card ${!member.website ? 'no-link' : ''}`}
                    {...cardProps}
                >
                    <img src={member.image.src} alt={member.name} class="member-image" />
                    <div class="member-info">
                        <h3 class="member-name">{member.name}</h3>
                        <div class="member-title">{member.title}</div>
                        <div class="member-details">
                            {member.major}
                        </div>
                        <div class="languages">
                            <strong>Favorite Languages:</strong> {member.favLanguages.join(", ")}
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </CardWrapper>
            );
        })}
    </div>

    <h2 class="subsection-title">Faculty Advisors</h2>
    <div class="board-grid">
        {facultyAdvisors.map(member => {
            const CardWrapper = member.website ? 'a' : 'div';
            const cardProps = member.website 
                ? { href: member.website, target: "_blank", rel: "noopener noreferrer" }
                : {};
            
            return (
                <CardWrapper 
                    class={`member-card ${!member.website ? 'no-link' : ''}`}
                    {...cardProps}
                >
                    <img src={member.image.src} alt={member.name} class="member-image" />
                    <div class="member-info">
                        <h3 class="member-name">{member.name}</h3>
                        <div class="member-title">{member.title}</div>
                        <div class="member-details">
                            {member.department}
                        </div>
                        <div class="languages">
                            <strong>Favorite Languages:</strong> {member.favLanguages.join(", ")}
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </CardWrapper>
            );
        })}
    </div>

	<!-- Add Sponsor Section here -->
	<!-- <h1 class="section-title">Sponsors</h1> -->
</main>
<Footer />
</body>
</html>

<style>
    .about-content {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 2rem;
    }

    .about-content p {
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .about-content a {
        color: var(--wolfpack-red);
        text-decoration: none;
    }

    .about-content a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
    }

    .board-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));
        gap: 2rem;
        margin: 2rem 0;
    }

    .member-card {
        background: white;
        border-radius: 12px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        overflow: hidden;
        transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        text-decoration: none !important;
        color: inherit;
        display: block;
    }

    .member-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-5px);
        box-shadow: 0 8px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        text-decoration: none !important;
    }

    .member-card.no-link {
        cursor: default;
    }

    .member-image {
        width: 100%;
        height: 300px;
        object-fit: cover;
        background: #f0f0f0;
    }

    .member-info {
        padding: 1.5rem;
    }

    .member-name {
        font-size: 1.4rem;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin: 0 0 0.25rem 0;
        color: #333;
    }

    .member-title {
        color: var(--wolfpack-red);
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .member-details {
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        color: #666;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .member-details strong {
        color: #333;
    }

    .languages {
        margin-top: 1rem;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        color: #666;
    }

    .languages strong {
        color: #333;
    }

    .section-title {
        font-size: 2rem;
        margin: 3rem 0 1rem 0;
        color: #333;
    }

    .subsection-title {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        margin: 2rem 0 1rem 0;
        color: #666;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .board-grid {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
    }
</style>